---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Housam.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I'm Housam. I write about code, math, research, and creative work.
    </p>
    <p>
      This blog is my personal publishing tool — built from scratch with
      <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and MDX.
      No CMS, no database, no dependencies I don't control.
    </p>

    <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Posts</strong> — articles about programming, systems, and ideas</li>
      <li><strong>Papers</strong> — research papers with summaries, abstracts, and downloadable PDFs</li>
      <li><strong>Notes</strong> — short-form notes, snippets, and references</li>
      <li><strong>Renders</strong> — 2D and 3D visual work with interactive viewers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      You can reach me by email at <a href="mailto:housam.kak20@gmail.com">housam.kak20@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
